The paper discusses medical image segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on optimization-based methods, which are often used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications. The paper also mentions the use of energy functionals, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural network (cs.NE) research.
